'''血管紧张素受体'''（{{lang-en|angiotensin receptors}}）是以[[血管紧张素|血管紧张素]]作为[[配体|配体]]的[[G蛋白偶联受体|G蛋白偶联受体]]。<ref name="pmid10977869">{{cite journal | author = de Gasparo M, Catt KJ, Inagami T, Wright JW, Unger T | title = International union of pharmacology. XXIII. The angiotensin II receptors | journal = Pharmacol. Rev. | volume = 52 | issue = 3 | pages = 415–72 | year = 2000 | pmid = 10977869 | doi =  | issn =  | url = http://pharmrev.aspetjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/52/3/415 | access-date = 2008-12-22 | archive-date = 2009-03-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090316180325/http://pharmrev.aspetjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/52/3/415 | dead-url = no }}</ref>它是[[肾素-血管紧张素系统|肾素-血管紧张素系统]]的重要组成部分。<ref name="pmid17346243">{{cite journal | author = Higuchi S, Ohtsu H, Suzuki H, Shirai H, Frank GD, Eguchi S| title = Angiotensin II signal transduction through the AT1 receptor: novel insights into mechanisms and pathophysiology | journal = Clin. Sci | volume = 112 | issue = 8 | pages = 417–28 | year = 2007 | pmid = 17346243 | doi = 10.1042/CS20060342| issn = }}</ref>

